      <title>阿克曼旗下美国封闭式基金计划下周首次公开募股 (IPO) 募资 20 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/ackman-s-us-closed-end-fund-psus-eyes-2-billion-in-ipo-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比尔·阿克曼 (Bill Ackman) 计划首次公开募股 (IPO) 美国封闭式基金，预计将募集 20 亿美元资金，这还不到这位亿万富翁对冲基金经理本月早些时候提出的募资目标的十分之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/ackman-s-us-closed-end-fund-psus-eyes-2-billion-in-ipo-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 12:48:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巨额牛市交易告终，基金撤出铜市 200 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/funds-pull-20-billion-from-copper-as-mega-bull-trade-unravels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自 5 月中旬以来，由于对中国需求的担忧加剧，基金经理已平仓了超过 200 亿美元的铜多头仓位，导致这种最重要的工业大宗商品之一的资金迅速流出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/funds-pull-20-billion-from-copper-as-mega-bull-trade-unravels</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 12:35:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
